    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/867120/extras/21013f07d4de69cfb69923a1d0dd5f1d.avif?t=1749283250\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/867120/extras/c6f035d9592dbc56074eb985901b57a2.poster.avif?t=1749283250\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/867120/extras/c6f035d9592dbc56074eb985901b57a2.webm?t=1749283250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/867120/extras/9a211b60f002b819e73ecaa250105e45.avif?t=1749283250\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有一个地方像幻影一样，时而显现，时而隐秘不见，如此反复变幻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王国的骑士赛莉雅，因为传闻村民会忽然失踪，特地前来调查。然而在这个迷宫一样的地方饥饿的恶魔泛滥成灾……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地牢里怪物肆虐，陷阱丛生。一个穿着白色束身衣的女人，冒险者们，一个穿着连帽衫的可疑男人，消失的村民们……他们是盟友还是劲敌？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赛莉雅又是否能否解开迷宫的奥秘，逃出生天？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■黑暗奇幻副本RPG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・无数的怪兽和陷阱袭击主人公塞莉雅</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・他们狡猾地企图抓住塞莉雅，有技巧地使用技能和物品等去找到解决方法吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是个要看清楚敌人、并找到战术的游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鲁莽的战斗方法会让主角陷于危险之中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■重视活动&amp;探索的设计</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　・有自动侧绘功能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　・固定交战机制</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　打倒了主线任务中的敌人后，不需要再交战来提升等级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　达成后的EX副本会变成要再度交战的战斗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此游戏主要以鼠标操作，但是副本的移动等推荐与键盘并用。</p>",
